data.description: This home is move in ready! Situated in the desirable Spring Grove Plantation.  Don't miss the opportunity, this beautiful home is waiting for your family.  From the elegant 9' full glass front door to the glimmering back door, this home echos Beauty!  Once you enter the welcoming foyer, this is only the beginning!   You are immediately graced with a beautiful eat in kitchen with a massive sit down granite island, upgraded gas stove, stainless steel fridge, staggered cabinets surrounding the stainless steel microwave. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and friends.  There is a ton of storage to include an amazing walk in pantry.  The garage is conveniently located right off the kitchen foreasy unloading of groceries!  Also on the first floor is the elegant oversized master suite with an equally huge tiled onsuite with double vanity, separate tub & shower and walk in closet.   The downstairs laundry room is conveniently located right off the master suite.  After you have completed your tour of the first floor, you head upstairs to find 4 more really oversized bedrooms, each with entry hall on opposite sides for added privacy, separated by a huge loft.   Kind of like having two totally separate main living spaces also with another full bath.  Now we go outside to the well manicured yard with full front porch and brick walk way, cozy screened porch for those lazy nights without the bugs.   The 2 car garage features convenient garage opener. This home is also conveniently located near all Charleston has to offer including Cypress Gardens (10 minutes), Joint Base Charleston, the Naval Weapons Station via Bushy Park, Boeing, Charleston International Airport, Bosch, (15/20 minutes), Downtown Charleston (20-30 minutes), and the beach of your choice- Isle of Palms, Folly Beach, or Sullivans Island (30-45 minutes).  To see this beauty and make it yours, Call now, this one won't last long!!!
